Text: Re Storage Deal and Cc Can you cut off deal going forward I am forwarding the message from Tommy Yanowski Let me know if this is a problem Thanks Karie Forwarded by Karie HastingsHOUECT on AM Enron Technology From Tommy J Yanowski AM To Karie CT cc Julie CT Subject Re Storage Deal and Karie Deal number should be the good deal Deal number is an interruptible storage deal and contract is an interruptible contract Storage deal is a firm storage deal Since it doesnt agree with the firmness of the contract I would probably cut off that deal going forward Tommy KARIE HASTINGS PM To Tommy J CT Julie CT cc Subject Storage Deal and Tommy There are two Storage deals that are using the same contract number Julie Meyers believes that deal is the correct deal but wants to check with you first since you put in deal Let me know when you look at them if we need to cut off or kill deal Thanks Karie Deal Contract

Storage Deal and Cc There are two Storage deals that are using the same contract number Can you look at the two deals and determine which one is the correct deal Do we need to kill or cut off the other deal Let me know when you get back in the office and look at it Karie Deal Contract
